{
  "stem": "19939.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 106.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember her walking to the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The son was supporting her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Her daughter-in-law and her daughter and their little baby, two years old, a little beautiful doll, beautiful doll with them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I see her walking bent, with the-- with the cane.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then she lie down on the bed, and she slept.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I felt, you know, the first time, my-- my-- my heart, how I was sorry for her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, and she was-- and she was old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then they had to go to-- they called the people, whoever had papers was allowed to stay, right, in the house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I had papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My stepmother was working outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father and all the others had to-- to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember the old people, right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now my-- my stepmother's father was a religious [? older, ?] I see it still now, he wasn't allowed to stay, right?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was his daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the fear of being caught, or maybe she wanted to protect, and he was facing her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wanted her to-- to hide him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a house that used to probably belong to some people that had horses or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had an outside, a big thing for wood and for coal, right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she could have-- somebody was hiding there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were found out, you know, behind-- because piles of wood for the winter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was facing him and she wouldn't-- you know, she didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she had to let him go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was so-- everybody was so helpless.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had her children to protect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we took everything so literally when they said, you're not allowed to go out, you're not allowed to shelter anybody.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we will be killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
